    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Melee Tactics Toolbox pg. 27</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can be placed only on reach weapons, piercing melee weapons, and weapons from the flail fighter weapon training group. When a sticky weapon scores a critical hit against a target, instead of rolling to confirm the critical threat, the wielder can deal normal damage and attempt a steal combat maneuver check against the target of the attack. This combat maneuver doesn't provoke an attack of opportunity, and the wielder gains a +2 bonus on the combat maneuver check.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, Improved Steal, <em>spider climb</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
